<|> 𝐖𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐢𝐬 𝐏𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐧 ?
      Python is an easy to understand , general purpose  and high level programming language. It design philosophy to emphasises code readability.
      It was developed by " 𝙂𝙪𝙞𝙙𝙤 𝙫𝙖𝙣 𝙍𝙤𝙨𝙨𝙪𝙢 " in 1991.

    Python is popular language because It is known for its simplicity , readability , and ease to use. It is an execellent choice for beginners as well as experienced programmers.

<|> 𝐀𝐝𝐯𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐧 
 Python is versatile and widely used in every technical field.

   > Easy to Code
   > Improve productivity
   > Vast library Support
   > A lot of career options for you
   > Used almost everywhere

      >> Interpreted Language --> Code is executed line by line without converting into object code.

      >> Platform independence --> It work on diffferent platform like windows , macOS , raspberry PI , etc.

      >> Free --> Python is free that anyone can use it by his own learning.

      >> Less code, more efficient --> Python syntax permit programmers to write code in less lines & create its interpretation faster.

